data.revised_prompt: Depict two individuals in a conversation within a contemporary office or lobby area. They are studying a folder containing documents. On the left stands a Caucasian man characterized by his short brown hair, glasses, and a light-colored shirt. On the right stands a South Asian woman with long dark hair and glasses, wearing a light blue blouse, and deep in thought with her hand on her chin. This scene showcases an architecturally modern setting, displaying large glass windows and a unique, circular light fixture made up of several rings overhead. There is a railing nearby, suggesting a mezzanine or second floor. Empower the image with a professional atmosphere indicative of a business dialogue or meeting. Render this in an art style reminiscent of pre-1912 Japanese ukiyo-e woodblock prints to align with the requested anime aesthetic.
